" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b42a3a8bdb9c92c59ef0c86c81c4d0a81d1f1944","tid":2099710,"uid":21486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T15:27:17.000Z","msg":"今日有唔少人因為條是非題中咗伏，又有唔少人唔識搵票站編碼，所以都係出返個簡單懶人包，入到票站直接比QR Code 同住址證明 1 分鐘就搞掂<br />\n<br />\n- 官方投票網址係 <a href=\"https://webapp.popvote.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwebapp.popvote.hk&d=68p4wiGQQ1h%2Fwz3iobjDK5gFNMRZLCTiZeA0y1vO9n4%3D&h=fa617098\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://webapp.popvote.hk</a><br />\n- 票站編號而家可以上 <a href=\"https://legco2020.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Flegco2020.com&d=68p4wiGQQ1h%2Fwz3iobjDK5gFNMRZLCTiZeA0y1vO9n4%3D&h=582a2886\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://legco2020.com</a> 查，但都係以官方 Excel 為準，可以同票站人員確認 (<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/&hellip;/1rTHp9g2UfTax1rQMgJEyQ6CEjH&hellip;/view\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2F%E2%80%A6%2F1rTHp9g2UfTax1rQMgJEyQ6CEjH%E2%80%A6%2Fview&d=68p4wiGQQ1h%2Fwz3iobjDK5gFNMRZLCTiZeA0y1vO9n4%3D&h=2425fc7f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/&hellip;/1rTHp9g2UfTax1rQMgJEyQ6CEjH&hellip;/view</a>)<br />\n- 超區選民一定要喺 #果條是非題 答「否」<br />\n- 填到最後見到 QR code，先帶埋住址證明入票站確認<br />\n<br />\n（咩話？仲未諗掂揀邊個？ 即上 <a href=\"https://legco2020.com/candidates\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Flegco2020.com%2Fcandidates&d=68p4wiGQQ1h%2Fwz3iobjDK5gFNMRZLCTiZeA0y1vO9n4%3D&h=ad4089bc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://legco2020.com/candidates</a>)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/o7HO9WN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fo7HO9WN.png&h=457d15db&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7dc837737ef83279b9a045f3e2798a78309fdb9d","tid":2099710,"uid":78574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T15:28:18.000Z","msg":"唔煩覆，唔駛排隊的話幾十秒搞掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"458818f0589d45e0d69565